import React from 'react';
import {
    Button,
    Card,
    Col,
    ListGroup,
    ListGroupItem,
    Row,
} from 'react-bootstrap';

function LoginScreen() {
    return (
        <>
            <Row>
                <Col md={3}>
                    
                </Col>
                <Col md={6}>
                    <Card>
                        <ListGroup variant='flush'>
                            <ListGroupItem>
                                <Button className='btn-block' type='button'>
                                    Sign In
                                </Button>
                            </ListGroupItem>
                            <ListGroupItem>
                                <Button className='btn-block' type='button'>
                                    Sign In
                                </Button>
                            </ListGroupItem>
                            <ListGroupItem>
                                <Button className='btn-block' type='button'>
                                    Sign In
                                </Button>
                            </ListGroupItem>
                        </ListGroup>
                    </Card>
                </Col>
            </Row>
        </>
    );
}

export default LoginScreen;
